and unfinished.

3
00:00:25,094 --> 00:00:28,097
Complicated by history
and counter-history

4
00:00:28,131 --> 00:00:30,513
with an urban fabric
that resists all attempts

5
00:00:30,547 --> 00:00:31,686
to reorder it.

6
00:00:31,721 --> 00:00:33,723
♪

7
00:00:33,757 --> 00:00:35,587
Berlin fascinates

8
00:00:35,621 --> 00:00:39,418
and people continue to be
drawn to its darkness

9
00:00:39,453 --> 00:00:41,765
and its light.

