00:28:02,853 --> 00:28:05,891
Joining the throngs
of frugal shoppers,

593
00:28:05,925 --> 00:28:07,202
Anton, Wolfgang, and I.

594
00:28:07,237 --> 00:28:09,515
We have some purchases in mind.

