00:34:49,949 --> 00:34:52,228
There's a place in Berlin where
they serve currywurst

742
00:34:52,262 --> 00:34:54,471
with champagne.
Really?

743
00:34:54,506 --> 00:34:58,130
Yeah, yeah, yeah. Champagne
always works obviously.

744
00:35:00,339 --> 00:35:01,789
Oh, I like this.
It's a good match.

745
00:35:01,823 --> 00:35:03,825
Super.

746
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:05,068
It's a cool place

747
00:35:05,103 --> 00:35:08,140
that you can come
and see movies like this.

748
00:35:09,555 --> 00:35:11,937
The film premiered in Berlin
in 1927

749
00:35:11,971 --> 00:35:14,595
presenting troubling issues
of its time.

750
00:35:14,629 --> 00:35:17,253
And it turns out, ours:
corporate greed,

751
00:35:17,287 --> 00:35:19,427
political corruption,
social inequality,

752
00:35:19,462 --> 00:35:21,774
and in a figure of
Brigitte Helm's Maria,

753
00:35:21,809 --> 00:35:24,950
the dangerous, yet powerful,
role of the individual activist

754
00:35:24,984 --> 00:35:27,470
in an oppressive culture.

755
00:35:27,504 --> 00:35:30,887
Her eyes, I mean,
she's a little cross-eyed.

756
00:35:30,921 --> 00:35:33,303
Yeah, but that's sexy, you know?

757
00:35:33,338 --> 00:35:34,787
Yeah.

